<para> Default value : 10</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>
<emphasis role="bold">fexp [1/(rad/s)] : Exponential decay of Stribeck effect</emphasis>
</para>
<para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1. </para>
<para> Default value : 2</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>
<emphasis role="bold">mode_start [-] : Initial sliding mode (-1=Backward, 0=Sticking, 1=Forward, 2=Free)</emphasis>
</para>
<para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1. </para>
<para> Default value : 0</para>
</listitem>
